## Layout — Landing Page

- Floating nav: `rounded-[28px]`, `max-w-5xl`, `shadow-card`
- Section cards: `rounded-[32px]`, `border`, `bg-forge-surface`, `shadow-card`
- Canvas mockup: `rounded-[28px]`, `border`, `shadow-card`
- CTA: `rounded-[32px]`, gradient bg

## Layout — Auth Pages

- Full-page `forge-bg`, floating nav pill `rounded-[20px]` at top
- Form card: `rounded-[28px]`, `shadow-card`, `p-8`
- Inputs: `h-12`, `rounded-xl`, `shadow-card`

## Component Patterns

### Floating Panel (universal pattern)

```tsx
<div className="rounded-[24px] border border-forge-border bg-forge-surface shadow-card p-4">
  {/* content */}
</div>
```

### Status Badge

```tsx
<span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-status-running text-forge-text">
  Running
</span>
```

### Sidebar Tree Item

```tsx
<button className={`w-full flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 rounded-xl text-[13px] transition-colors ${
  isSelected
    ? "bg-forge-amber-bg text-forge-text font-medium"
    : "text-forge-text-secondary hover:bg-forge-surface-2"
}`}>
```

### Bottom Floating Toolbar

```tsx
<div className="pointer-events-none fixed bottom-5 left-1/2 z-40 flex -translate-x-1/2 items-center gap-4">
  <button className="pointer-events-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-forge-border bg-forge-surface shadow-card" />
  <div className="pointer-events-auto flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full border border-forge-border bg-forge-surface px-4 py-3 shadow-panel">
    {/* tool icons separated by w-px dividers */}
  </div>
  <button className="pointer-events-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-forge-border bg-forge-surface shadow-card" />
</div>
```

### Input Field

```tsx
<input className="h-12 w-full rounded-xl border border-forge-border bg-forge-surface px-4 text-forge-text shadow-card transition-all placeholder:text-forge-text-dim focus:border-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/30" />
```

## Conventions

- **Floating cards everywhere**: Every panel, form, nav, section is a floating rounded card
- Prefer CSS variables via Tailwind classes over inline `style={{ }}` props
- Use `cn()` from `clsx`/`tailwind-merge` for conditional classes
- All interactive elements: `cursor-pointer`, visible focus ring
- File naming: kebab-case for files, PascalCase for components
- Icons: Phosphor for workspace (size 16-18), Lucide for landing (size 20-24)
